Package: ggseg.formats
Title: Utility package for the ggseg-packages
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Athanasia Mo", "Mowinckel", , "a.m.mowinckel@psykologi.uio.no", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5756-0223"))
Description: The ggseg, ggseg3d and ggsegExtra packages rely on common
    base formats, which are contained in this package. It serves as the
    main base dependency for the other packages in this suite.
